            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "also why you cannot solve a quadratic equation by taking the square root of both sides.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "Inequalities-to-do-with-circles",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Inequalities to do with circles",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "If you rearrange the equation of a circle to obtain a function for how far a point (x, y) is from the center:",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code" : [
            "f(x, y) = (x - a)^2 + (y - b)^2"
          ],
          "syntax" : "math",
          "type" : "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "You can then use this function to determine whether a point is inside, outside, or on the circle.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code" : [
            "f(x, y) < r^2 \\implies \\text{inside}",
            "f(x, y) = r^2 \\implies \\text{on (this is also the standard form)}",
            "f(x, y) > r^2 \\implies \\text{outside}"
          ],
          "syntax" : "math",
          "type" : "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "The area bound between two circles, where one circle is inside the other, is given by:",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code" : [
            "A = \\pi(R^2 - r^2)"
          ],
          "syntax" : "math",
          "type" : "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "where:",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items" : [
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "code" : "$R$",
                      "type" : "codeVoice"
                    },
